November 12, 1944

This house holds on to souls for a lifetime. I thought I had given it to my husband when I vowed to love him until the end of time.
I lied.
Nothing could have prepared me for the day my phantom appeared outside my window. He was terrifying, yet hypnotizing, and I couldn’t deny my intrigue.
